<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="U" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Untainted" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Untainted,</orth> 1) undefiled: <bibl n="shak. luc 1710" default="NO" valid="yes">Lucr. 1710</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. luc 1710" default="NO" valid="yes">Lucr. 1710</bibl> <bibl n="shak. mm 3.1.264" default="NO" valid="yes">Meas. III, 1, 264</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 2h6 3.2.232" default="NO" valid="yes">H6B III, 2, 232</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r3 3.1.7" default="NO" valid="yes">R3 III, 1, 7</bibl>.<lb />2) uninjured: <cit><quote>him in thy course u. do allow for beauty's pattern to succeeding men,</quote> <bibl n="shak. son 19.11" default="NO" valid="yes">Sonn. 19, 11</bibl></cit>.
<lb />3) not charged with a crime: <cit><quote>u., unexamined, free, at liberty,</quote> <bibl n="shak. r3 3.6.9" default="NO" valid="yes">R3 III, 6, 9</bibl></cit>.
